Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Death of Elvis, August 1977
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b0407j97
Last Broadcast Date: Wed 21 Sep 1977
Death of Elvis. Carter's move away from liberal promises. Disquiet among black voters about Carter. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014. Show less